      "widgets_values": [
        "# MODELS AND NODES USED IN THIS WORKFLOW  \n\n---\n\n### Put all models in the models folder, organized into their respective subfolders. \n### If a required folder doesn’t exist, create it.\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Unet Loader GGUF (NEEDS 2 MODELS)  \nDownload **wan2.2_i2v_A14b_high_noise_lightx2v_4step-Q6_K.gguf** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/jayn7/WAN2.2-I2V_A14B-DISTILL-LIGHTX2V-4STEP-GGUF/resolve/main/high_noise/wan2.2_i2v_A14b_high_noise_lightx2v_4step-Q6_K.gguf)  \n\nand also\n\nDownload **/wan2.2_i2v_A14b_low_noise_lightx2v_4step-Q6_K.gguf** from\n[HERE](https://huggingface.co/jayn7/WAN2.2-I2V_A14B-DISTILL-LIGHTX2V-4STEP-GGUF/resolve/main/low_noise/wan2.2_i2v_A14b_low_noise_lightx2v_4step-Q6_K.gguf)\n\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/wan2.2`  \n\nOr download **Different Q version** depending on your VRAM from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/jayn7/WAN2.2-I2V_A14B-DISTILL-LIGHTX2V-4STEP-GGUF/tree/main)  \n\n---  \n\n## 🟣 Load CLIP  \nDownload **umt5_xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Wan_2.1_ComfyUI_repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/umt5_xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors?download=true)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders`  \n\n---  \n\n## 🟣 Load VAE  \nDownload **wan_2.1_vae.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Wan_2.1_ComfyUI_repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/vae/wan_2.1_vae.safetensors?download=true)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`  \n\n---  \n\n## 🟣 Load Lora \nDownload **highnoise.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/NikolaSigmoid/wan2.2-i2v-loras-eye-in/resolve/main/highnoise.safetensors)  \n\n### Rename it to eye-highnoise.safetensors\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/loras/wan2.2`  \n\n---\n\n## 🧩 Nodes Installed from Manager  \n\n- **ComfyUI-GGUF**\n- **ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite**\n- **ComfyUI-Easy-Use**\n\n---\n\n## 📚 Resources  \n🎥 **Tutorials:** [Pixaroma YouTube Channel](https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma) 